  "Metadata" -> {
   "built" -> "{2026, 4, 12, 17, 58, 21.992150}", 
    "history" -> {"12", "", "", ""}, "context" -> "QuantumMob`Q3`", 
    "keywords" -> {}, "specialkeywords" -> {}, 
    "tutorialcollectionlinks" -> {}, "index" -> True, "label" -> 
    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "TheRotation[\\[Phi], 0] returns the 2*2 identity matrix. \
TheRotation[\\[Phi], \\[Mu]] returns the 2*2 matrix representing the rotation \
by angle \\[Phi] around the \\[Mu]th axis. Here \\[Mu] = 1 indicates the \
x-axis, \\[Mu] = 2, the y-axis, and \\[Mu] = 3, the z-axis. \
TheRotation[{\\[Phi], \\[Mu]}] is equivalent to TheRotation[\\[Phi], \\[Mu]]. \
TheRotation[{\\[Phi]1, \\[Mu]1}, {\\[Phi]2, \\[Mu]2}, ...] is equivalent to \
TheRotation[\\[Phi]1, \\[Mu]1]\\[CircleTimes]TheRotation[\\[Phi]2, \\[Mu]2\\ \
]\\[CircleTimes].... TheRotation[\\[Phi], {x, y, z}] returns the 2*2 matrix \
representing the rotation by angle \\[Phi] round the axis {x, y, z}. \
TheRotation[{\\[Phi]1, {x1, x2, x2}}, {\\[Phi]2, {x2, y2, z2}}, ...] is \
equivalent to TheRotation[\\[Phi]1, {x1, y1, \
z1}]\\[CircleTimes]TheRotation[\\[Phi]2, {x2, y2, z2}]\\[CircleTimes].... \
TheRotation[\\[Phi], {j, \\[Mu]}] returns the matrix representing the \
rotation by angle \\[Phi] around the \\[Mu]th axis for Spin = j. \
TheRotation[{\\[Phi]1, {j1, \\[Mu]1}}, {\\[Phi]2, {j2, \\[Mu]2}}, \\ ...] is \
equivalent to TheRotation[\\[Phi]1, {j1, \\[Mu]1}]\\[CircleTimes]TheRotation[\
\\[Phi]1, \\ {j1, \\[Mu]1}]\\[CircleTimes]....", "synonyms" -> {}, 
    "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "TheRotation", "titlemodifier" -> "", 
    "metadescription" -> "", "windowtitle" -> "TheRotation", "type" -> 
    "Symbol", "uri" -> "QuantumMob/Q3/ref/TheRotation"}},
